title: Vostek- Favorite Things 2002-2006 (2008) FLAC audio
description:
Vostek has been making electronic music for over 10 years. This is collection of his favorite compositions in pristine full-spectrum lossless quality sound.

Vostek is an acronym for Variable Oscillating Sensory Technology. 

Vostek also wields the art of video and performs as a VJ at parties, festivals, and other events of celebration.

Visit www.VSTK.org for more information, pictures, music, video, and contact information.

Vostek says its good to share and share-alike. 

We beam through light in our Pirate Space Vessels.
